    "name": "[Baseline] loan-origination-api",
    "description": "API for managing loan application origination, underwriting decisions, and\ndocument collection in the Lending domain. This service handles the full\nlifecycle from application submission through approval or denial.\n\n**Authentication:**\n- Service-to-service: mTLS (mutual TLS)\n- Internal gateway: JWT token (Bearer token)\n\n**Rate Limits:**\n- Standard: 200 requests/minute\n- Batch operations: 50 requests/minute\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Lending Platform Team\n Email: lending-platform@example.com",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
